data.value: TPM management department has completed construction of a multi-storey car park where allow people who work around the TPM new car park to park their car. The car park can accommodate a total of 200 cars, where each level will have 50 parking spaces. There are no people or systems manage the new car park, it will be mess if there is no systems manage the car park. Therefore, to manage the cars to park there, this system developed for the car park in order to makes everything organised nicely.
